"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:25:35.000Z","msg":"我諗係頭兩件合併？但依家事主應該係驚第二件多d"},{"pid":"965b9689798148e20a9c3b1a2e475648a6a17c22","tid":1897484,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"C+偵探"},{"pid":"a1edd0d783f61cccb36c33180d1adc9d668a8be8","tid":1897484,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"點解起身知道物件有動過，覺得有可疑唔錄片錄低自己訓覺時發生左咩？"},{"pid":"43163802fa6569c115e95e82496ead3f6d5415ff","tid":1897484,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"似精神有問題多"},{"pid":"f88d3a5edddb56f63132495e4e2ada35c969a982","tid":1897484,"uid":152720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1edd0d783f61cccb36c33180d1adc9d668a8be8","tid":1897484,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"點解起身知道物件有動過，覺得有可疑唔錄片錄低自己訓覺時發生左咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:33:52.000Z","msg":"拍電影咩 好恐怖"},{"pid":"dfd6b3a63e6ee0a2b51496a7f7314df0b8c8ec87","tid":1897484,"uid":156587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88d3a5edddb56f63132495e4e2ada35c969a982","tid":1897484,"uid":152720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1edd0d783f61cccb36c33180d1adc9d668a8be8","tid":1897484,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"點解起身知道物件有動過，覺得有可疑唔錄片錄低自己訓覺時發生左咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:33:52.000Z","msg":"拍電影咩 好恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34420bd8de0315e02157b70186955843889487fa","tid":1897484,"uid":15948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T19:49:13.000Z","msg":"諗起隻狗吠個鬼故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcb74a1af9ce5fa537c45c8c350e951bd8d68c4","tid":1897484,"uid":45652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"嗯 全部鬼故元素都有齊哂"},{"pid":"1f23c0a5e672f109da87c7f1cbf094fdd5f9a8b4","tid":1897484,"uid":169433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb8de63a9e892f97a8fdb5296e091e9307d724c","tid":1897484,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"推 轉開係學術台會比較好"},{"pid":"6ffff6746f55ed9343faae3fbc6e8cfffe7f2a87","tid":1897484,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"定故黎架"},{"pid":"608774bd579c4fd6110b2119b7395267afc038ee","tid":1897484,"uid":169433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f622abc753d4902d7c56d92958e17a79dc0ca4e","tid":1897484,"uid":169433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392df6e025a47689455df3b35baf779790c8ef7b","tid":1897484,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"搵恐怖在線Edmond，佢識好多泰國師傅"},{"pid":"bc4219c86c850e9281edddea170db5b67c927b27","tid":1897484,"uid":170277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ffff6746f55ed9343faae3fbc6e8cfffe7f2a87","tid":1897484,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"定故黎架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:45:31.000Z","msg":"可以㩒返入上面條link睇下 我見po主都好詳細咁講返同有文有路 所以我諗應該唔係故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2d312a2dc3138c2ccf0a5f345c0765cb933013","tid":1897484,"uid":170277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88d3a5edddb56f63132495e4e2ada35c969a982","tid":1897484,"uid":152720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1edd0d783f61cccb36c33180d1adc9d668a8be8","tid":1897484,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"點解起身知道物件有動過，覺得有可疑唔錄片錄低自己訓覺時發生左咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:33:52.000Z","msg":"拍電影咩 好恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"po主話已經搬走左，但件事未完所以都諗緊要唔要搬返去住再裝cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e3fb532c947c47988c709da47b22a2147f3fae","tid":1897484,"uid":169433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}